OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCovid: Classroom masks in  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FEngland for no longer than 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fnecessary, Nadhim Zahawi   
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Secondary students in England will wear
OL,6, masks in classrooms "not for a day     
OL,7, longer than necessary", Nadhim Zahawi  
OL,8, has said.                              
OL,10,FThe education secretary defended the   
OL,11,Frequirement to wear masks during       
OL,12,Flessons, as Omicron cases surge.       
OL,14,FHe added ministers are determined to   
OL,15,Fkeep schools open after learning a     
OL,16,F"painful lesson" from earlier closures.
OL,18,FMr Zahawi also repeated assurances that
OL,19,Fnothing in recent Covid data suggests  
OL,20,Fnew curbs are needed.                  
